    "Based on the calculation, the cohesion (C) = 11.98 MPa and friction angle (φ) = 42.23°. The linear regression shows good fit (R² = 0.964) confirming the validity of Mohr-Coulomb criterion for this sandstone.\n",
    "We see that the samples become stronger as the confinement pressure increases as the sigma 1 (value at failure) increases. "
